      void MessageHandle.setReplyTo(Destination destination)
      * Performance Tip: If your application is setting the ReplyTo address on many messages to the same destination or set of destinations consider using NativeDestinationHandle to create a set of NativeDestination objects that can be re-used.

    • Uses of Destination in com.solacesystems.solclientj.core.resource

      Subinterfaces of Destination in com.solacesystems.solclientj.core.resource 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      interface  Queue
      Objects with the Queue interface can represent a guaranteed delivery queue on the solace appliance, either as a target (Destination) or as a Endpoint for a consumer flow (FlowHandle).
      interface  Topic
      Objects with the Topic Interface represent a solace topic.
